item.title: How to make a account
item.dc:creator: @Punkzombie Punkzombie
item.description:
@Punkzombie wrote:

download your source and client… load them up… enter the username and password of your choice and it will automatically create the account… after a certain amount of time your account will save… now go to the character folder in your source and double click on your account… you will see something like this…

[code][ACCOUNT]
character-username = test
character-password = test

[CHARACTER]
character-height = 0
character-posx = 2537
character-posy = 4715
character-rights = 0
character-lastconnection = localhost
character-special = 50
character-tz = -1
character-starter = 1
character-pouch1 = 0
character-pouch2 = 0
character-pouch3 = 0
character-pouch4 = 0
character-energy = 100
character-taskID = -1
character-taskAmount = -1
character-jad = 0
character-q1 = 15
character-q2 = 15
character-q3 = 15
character-q4 = 15
character-q5 = 15
character-q6 = 15
character-q7 = 15
character-q8 = 15
character-q9 = 15
character-q10 = 15
character-q11 = 15
character-war = 0
character-warj =0
character-warm =0
character-Ahrim = 0
character-Verac = 0
character-Dharok =0
character-Torag = 0
character-Karils =0
character-Guthan =0
character-Barrows 0
character-brightness = 0
character-fighttype = 2
character-skill = 2
character-chat = 1
character-ancients = 0
character-pin = 0
character-saradomin = 0
character-retaliate = 0
character-action = 0
character-pcpoints = 99425
character-assault = 99849
character-donator = 1
character-bow = 100
character-shield = 100
character-rating = 1
character-donorPoints = 9989
character-tradeTimer = 0
[/code]
change the character rights near the top to 3 for owner… 2 for admin… 1 for mod… and keep 0 for regular player…
go to the tutorial section to learn more about editing servers…
